---
title: Chicken Ragù and Fusilli with Shredded Parmesan
description: This easy dinner features a savoury ragù sauce of quick cooking ground chicken, mirepoix and balsamic vinegar. Hearty fusilli pasta gets that delicious sauce in every nook and cranny, while umami-filled Parmesan cheese will have people asking for seconds!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragu-au-poulet-et-fusillis-83304b97.jpg
